# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different OS, lock file might cause issue.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is of high value.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock is of high value.
# pdm.lock

